@MPAAss I checked and noticed that too...that episode is unwatchable. Have not watched all episodes yet, but am midway through season 2 and it's perfect so far, thanks a bunch Toilet_sniffer_V!

@xidio make sure you looking at the seasons and not the season within the extras folder....

@wino4life Yeah, there are so many programs that are great but...making DVD's out of this wouldn't be great. For example, season 4 is 5.45 gigs, 1 gig too much for a standard dvd disk. 

My solution was to convert the files using mkv2vob (free application, no need to use piratebay for it). They come out perfect quality. Stream to my tv through PS3, done. Not to mention, the conversion only takes about 30 sec / episode.
